title: "Ontology of LLM-Based Agentic AI"
abstract: >-
  An OWL 2 ontology providing a framework-independent, reasoner-verifiable
  conceptual model for Large Language Model (LLM) based agent systems,
  aligned with the OASIS 2 foundational agent ontology.
